				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Howdy,
<br />

<br />
I just made the discovery that I can reliably run 2 accounts on my system, and have resurrected my mage alt.  Once I get a few more lvls, I should be able to group the 2 together.  What pets do people duoing this combo use?  Any other strategies to be aware of?
<br />

<br />
Here's the obvious benefits:
<br />
DPS - kill harder mobs, kill mobs faster
<br />
Poss. root w/ earth pet
<br />
Stuns w/ monk pet
<br />
Nukes to stop runners
<br />
Damage shields
<br />
Another person to Bind Wounds on my beast <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" />
<br />
Pet goodies
<br />

<br />
Are there any other benefits that I'm missing?  How should this affect our strategies?  does the fire pet's DPS pull agro from our pet?
<br />

<br />
My BST just hit 46.  I have been told that I can group w/ a lvl30 char...is this the min lvl?
<br />

<br />
Curious, and finally planar,
<br />
Khauruk</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
