			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Dunno much about boxing a mage.  I'm only boxed traditional support classes.  Druids/shamans/clerics.  Druid is perfect for me and my Beast.  The snares, DS, ports, buffs, dots, nukes, and small pet  <img src="images/smiles/icon_lol.gif" alt="Laughing" border="0" /> ...make him a 9.999 on the hotboxin scale.
<br />

<br />
If you are worried about agro, just take off the /pet taunt on the mage pet and leave it *on* the Beastlord pet.  As far as grouping with a level 30 @ level 46, it can be done but it might be more beneficial to power the mage to about 40 or so, which can be done fairly easily in the Overthere.  My experience with mage pets is that the 3 pets worth the money pre-50's is the Air and Earth pets.  Air stuns, Water Backstabs and Earth roots.
<br />

<br />
Hope this helps. <img src="images/smiles/icon_rolleyes.gif" alt="Rolling Eyes" border="0" /><br />_________________<br />========&gt;Sqeeter Giturdone&lt;========
