				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Mage/BL combo is alot of fun. right now i have my 68 BST and my 67 mage together. However i two box, i dont run both on the same computer so there is a completly different dynamic there. However you dont have to worry about playing pet cleric if youlike to tank. just always position the pets behind the mob you are taking. you get more stuns that way it seems and dmg is higher. water pet is good then for backstab, however i find i take less dmg using air pet. you can effectivly duo the turkeybees in BoT when you get to the right level (stormriders). Mage is alot of fun and you have to love the pet toys and that mod rod  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /> Before they made mobs re-mitigate slow in OoW, i was duoing those mobs as well. You can have alot of fun and you'll enjoy the dps, so will groups that you join in. enjoy</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
