<br />

<br />
AthlonXP 1.5gig, 512MB RAM, Radeon9000, 1 hard drive.  I've the main instance running at 1024x768 windowed w/ most everything turned on...spell effects are only on near though, at medium setting.  2nd instance runs off of a separate folder, 800x600, 1/2 of the models off, nosound.txt in the folder, far clip plane at minimum to see, no sky, no special lighting, or any of that.  Minimal lag w/ one in bazaar, one in PoK. Zoning does take forever though...we'll see how that improves w/ addition of another HD on the other IDE channel.  I haven't tried WinEQ, EQPlayNice or any of those programs yet.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
