				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Duo with my 63 mage a fair bit.. I like to use the air pet as I find the warder proc stun, + air pet stun keep casters in line alot more as well as cutting down on how much time mobs have to swing at me and the air pet seems to have higher AC than other pets in case I need it to offtank another mob (which is actually feasible when it's slowed).
<br />

<br />
Play both on the same box.. for the most part my mage has a few quick hotkeys.. one to assist me.  One to assist me and sent pet in.  The regular pet assortment and 2 or 3 for nukes of various kinds.. super DPS addition.  My advice though... if you do it, get the mage a mount <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="Wink" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
